INTRO                                             You see a scholarly looking merchant walking the dungeon.                                                                                                                                               NAME                                              "I am called Jonny, the traveling merchant."                                                                                                                                                            JOB                                               "Well, I used to sell armor, but me stock's too low. Now I've become a          HUNTER of rare artifacts."                                                                                              BYE                                               "Take care."                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              "Sorry. Don't know."                                                                                                                                                                                    HUNTER                                            "Yes, I hope to findeth things of value, so I canst peddle me goods once        again."                                                                                                                 SNAKE                                             "The snake! Ah yes! A snake once led me to a strange THING."                                                                                                                                            THING                                             He leans closer and whispers: "'Twas a magic POTION!"                                                                                                                                                   POTION                                            "Yes, I gave it to George over on the eastern area. Mayhap he still has it.     You ought to ask him. Remember, he thinks it came from a GRYPHON."                                                      GRYPHON                                           "'Tis strange, since we hath no gryphons here in the underland. Just ask him    about the gryphon. 'Tis actually the snake we both saw."                                                                